data.description: Reduced because seller wants an offer!  This home has everything you need for sure from location, upgrades, updated kitchen, space, and storage.  This 4 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath home greets you upon entry with the front porch, and a 2-story foyer entry and heavy molding columns create a stately greeting. Upon entry, a separate living room/office/playroom with custom built-in cabinets, and a separate dining room with a tray ceiling and great natural lighting graces the room.  A chef's newly updated kitchen with granite countertops and backsplash, a large island with plenty of countertop seating,  all overlooking the family room with a fireplace.  Upstairs are all 4 bedrooms that are really great size.  The large owner's suite features a tray ceiling and ensuite bath graced with dual vanities, a garden tub, and a separate shower.  Upstairs large laundry room has built-in cabinets and shelves. The level & fenced backyard with a flagstone oversized patio gives you that extra private backyard space you need for lots of entertaining, cookouts, or enjoying nature.  Lakeshore subdivision also offers swim and tennis amenities.  Lakeshore is close to Ashley Park, walking trails, Piedmont/Newnan Hospital, 2 minutes away from restaurants/grocery, 30 minutes from the Atlanta airport, and just 5 minutes from downtown Newnan offering quaint restaurants, shops, movies, and concerts on the lawn. Just 9 minutes away you will find Carl Miller Park offering a tree-shaded park with open fields, 2 playgrounds, a kid-friendly splash pad & walking paths.  Don't miss this opportunity.
